  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为这个事件溯源演示系统画一张上下文图。核心是一个叫\"Event Sourcing Demo\"的系统，它让用户可以创建和列出事件以及事件处理器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "systemA",
        "Event Sourcing Demo"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。那使用这个系统的用户有哪些类型？我需要确定Person节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "userA",
        "userB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "有两类用户。一类是\"System User\"，他们可以修改和查询系统中的对象。另一类是\"Designer\"，他们有权限创建事件类型和处理器。这两类人都需要和核心系统交互。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "userA",
        "System User",
        "userB",
        "Designer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以System User和Designer都是Person，分别对应userA和userB。那他们和Event Sourcing Demo系统的关系怎么描述？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "userA",
        "userB",
        "systemA",
        "Rel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "System User是\"Uses\"，就是普通使用系统。Designer是\"Designs\"，强调他们设计事件类型和处理器的能力。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Rel(userA, systemA, \"Uses\")",
        "Rel(userB, systemA, \"Designs\")"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加两条关系线。现在来看系统内部，Event Sourcing Demo需要依赖哪些外部或内部系统？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EventStore",
        "EventAPI",
        "EventUI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "内部有三个关键组件。Event Store是数据库，存所有事件；Event API提供接口；Event UI是用户界面。Event Store应该是外部数据库类型，API和UI是普通系统。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EventStore",
        "EventAPI",
        "EventUI",
        "SystemDb_Ext",
        "System"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，Event Store用SystemDb_Ext，Event API和Event UI都用System，对吧？这三个都放在哪里，和核心系统是什么包含关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "b1",
        "Event Boundary"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "这三个组件应该放在一个子边界里，叫\"Event Boundary\"，表示它们是事件相关的技术基础设施。这个边界嵌套在更大的企业边界内。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "b1",
        "Event Boundary",
        "Enterprise_Boundary"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，创建了b1边界包含Event Store、Event API和Event UI。那最外层的企业边界叫什么名字？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "b0",
        "EventBoundary0"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "外层边界叫\"EventBoundary0\"，包含整个演示系统的所有元素——两个用户角色、核心系统，以及刚才那个Event Boundary子边界。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "b0",
        "EventBoundary0",
        "userA",
        "userB",
        "systemA",
        "b1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
